extends layout

block content
	div.col-12.col-sm-12
		div.row
			div.index-wrapper
				img.header-image(src="/images/header-image-v2.png" alt="header-image")
				div.container
					div.searchfield
						form(action="/searches/search" method="post" autocomplete="off")
								h1.text-center What hashtag would you like to explore?
								br
								div.form-group
									div.input-group
										input.form-control(type="text" name="q" placeholder="e.g. #Donaldtrump" required)
										span.input-group-btn
											button.btn.btn-success(type="submit") Search
	div.container
		br
		h2.text-center We measure real-time emotion on Twitter using emojis.
			br
			br
			div.row
				div.col-12.col-sm-12.col-md-4.col-lg-4
					.reason
						h3 Powerful Data
							.emoji 💪📊
						p It's not easy to analyze emotional sentiment online, but our research and algorithms have allowed us to create the Emoji Analysis search tool specifically for Twitter hashtags. The search results will reveal how positive, negative and neutral any inquiries are. And the conclusions may just surprise you.
						a(href='/faq' id='reason-link') Our Research
				div.col-12.col-sm-12.col-md-4.col-lg-4
					.reason
						h3 Unearth Opinion
							.emoji 🌎🔝
						p Curious how others view current events? Interested in how well a campaign is stacking up? What about trending topics... Do you really think that you're the best judge? Our search tool gives you complete access to powerful information to use however you please. Hashtag away!
						a(href='/about' id='reason-link') About Us
				div.col-12.col-sm-12.col-md-4.col-lg-4
					.reason
						h3 Free to Use
							.emoji 😍💯
						p Unlike our money-hungry competitors, our search algorithm is free to use. All you need to do is create an account and you can get to searching as many times as you'd like! We guarantee we will never send annoying emails or invade your. We've done all the legwork, so just have fun 🎉!
						a(href='/faq' id='reason-link') Sign Up Here